    <j.2:build_info>cdm:CDM_2.1.7  tdm:1523  xslt:3945 saxon:9.0.0.1J JVM:1.6.0_29 metaconvJar:1.1.9 builddate:13/02/2014 11:40:02</j.2:build_info>
