    <j.0:event_legal_uses_concept_type_decision rdf:resource="http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/fd_602/1025"/>
    <j.0:event_legal_part_of_dossier rdf:resource="http://publications.europa.eu/resource/pegase/178830"/>
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/cdm#event"/>
    <j.0:event_legal_comment xml:lang="en">Eight amendments were adopted by Parliament. The third and last amendments suggest to delete the reference to final importation. The Commission is supportive to these amendments and it will modify its proposal accordingly.For the fifth and seventh amendment concerning the definition of natural gas and the services of accession to the distribution networks, the contents can be accepted. &amp;#13;
Finally, the other four amendments (first, second, fourth and sixth), which form part of a package, aim at opening the special regime for taxation for re-sellers to all taxable persons. It is not be possible to take into account </j.0:event_legal_comment>
    <j.0:initiated_by rdf:resource="http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/corporate-body/COM"/>
